## 5. User Roles

| Role | ID | Description |
|---|---|---|
| **Seeker** | `SEEKER` | Homeowner looking for interior design services |
| **Company** | `COMPANY` | Interior design company offering services |
| **Admin** | Phone in `ADMIN_PHONES` list | Platform admin with full dashboard access |

---

## 6. Core Features

### 6.1 Authentication & Onboarding

#### Phone OTP Authentication
- India-only (+91) phone number sign up/login
- Firebase Phone Auth with invisible reCAPTCHA
- 6-digit OTP verification with auto-submit
- 30-second resend countdown
- Duplicate account detection (checks both `seekers` and `companies` collections)

#### Role Selection
- Bottom sheet modal after OTP verification
- Two roles: "I need Home Interior" (Seeker) or "I am an Interior Company" (Company)

#### Profile Setup (Multi-step Wizard)

**Seeker Profile (2 Steps):**
1. **About You:** Name, avatar upload, city, property type (1-4+ BHK, Villa, Office)
2. **Preferences:** Space type (Residential/Commercial), rooms to design, budget range (₹3L–₹20L+), timeline

**Company Profile (3 Steps):**
1. **Company Info:** Company name, tagline, logo, city, years in business
2. **Services:** Service categories, specializations (8 options)
3. **Portfolio:** Upload up to 6 images, description, projects completed, budget range

---

### 6.2 Main App Interface (4-Tab Navigation)

The home screen features a bottom navigation bar with 4 tabs:

#### Tab 1: Explore (Swipe Discovery)
- **Tinder-style swipe deck** of profiles
- Seekers see companies; companies see seekers
- **Swipe right** → Like / Request meeting
- **Swipe left** → Pass
- **Tap** → View detailed profile
- **Meet button** → Direct meeting request (opens chat with meeting modal)
- Profile cards show: avatar, name/company, tagline, city, rating, services
- Empty state with refresh button when no profiles available

#### Tab 2: Find Connections
- Grid view of **all platform users** (opposite role)
- Search and filter functionality
- Meeting status badges (Pending, Scheduled, Confirmed, etc.)
- Quick action buttons: Chat or Request Meeting
- Filter options: All, Met, Pending, New

#### Tab 3: Chat (Real-time Messaging)
- **Chat List:** All conversations sorted by last message time
- **Individual Chat:** Real-time messaging via Firestore `onSnapshot`
- In-chat actions:
  - Schedule a meeting
  - Start a project
  - Submit a review
  - View meeting status
  - View project status
- Chat header shows partner's avatar, name, and role
- Message timestamps and read indicators

#### Tab 4: Profile
- User profile display with stats (matches, meetings, projects)
- Navigation to sub-pages:
  - **Edit Profile** — Update all profile fields, avatar, portfolio
  - **Wallet** — View balance, transactions, top-up
  - **Meetings** — View and manage all meetings
  - **Projects** — View and manage all projects
  - **Liked Profiles** — See profiles you've liked
  - **Notifications** — In-app notification center
  - **Privacy & Security** — Privacy settings
  - **App Settings** — Delete account, preferences
  - **Help & Support** — FAQ and contact info

---

### 6.3 Meetings System

#### Meeting Lifecycle
```
Request → Pending → Accepted → Scheduled → Confirmed/Denied
                     ↓
                  Declined
                     ↓
                  Cancelled
```

- **Schedule Meeting:** Select date, time, location from chat
- **Accept/Decline:** Meeting recipient can accept or decline
- **Confirm/Deny:** After meeting time passes, both parties confirm attendance
- **Reschedule:** Modify scheduled meetings with new date/time
- **Wallet Integration:** Meeting confirmation triggers wallet transactions (rewards for seekers)

#### Meeting Card Details
- Partner name and role
- Date, time, and location
- Status badges with color coding
- Confirmation badges showing both-party status

---

### 6.4 Wallet System

#### Company Wallet
- **Top-up via Razorpay** (₹500 to ₹50,000 presets + custom amount)
- Balance tracking (available + locked)
- Transaction history with status/reason labels
- Payment verification via server-side API

#### Seeker Wallet
- **Earnings** from confirmed meetings (reward system)
- Total earned, available balance, locked balance tracking
- **Withdrawal** via WhatsApp (manual process)
- Transaction history with earning breakdowns

#### Razorpay Integration (Server-side API)
- `POST /api/razorpay/create-order` — Create payment order
- `POST /api/razorpay/verify-payment` — Verify payment signature and credit wallet

---

### 6.5 Projects System

#### Project Lifecycle
```
Initiated → Accepted → Advance Paid → In Progress → Completed
```

- **Start Project:** From chat — specify project type, budget, description
- **Accept Project:** Company accepts with estimated cost
- **Advance Payment:** Upload payment screenshot, amount tracking
- **Timeline View:** Visual timeline showing project milestones
- **Status Tracking:** Color-coded status badges

---

### 6.6 Reviews & Ratings

- **Star Rating** (1–5 stars)
- **Written Review** with text feedback
- Review types: `MEETING` or `PROJECT`
- Reviews displayed on company profile detail view
- One review per meeting/project per user (duplicate prevention)

---

### 6.7 Profile Detail View

- Full-screen profile overlay with all details
- Avatar, name, tagline, city, rating
- Company-specific: Years in business, services, specializations, portfolio gallery, reviews
- Seeker-specific: Property type, rooms, budget, timeline
- Like/Pass action buttons
- Verified badge display

---

## 7. Admin Dashboard

The admin dashboard (`/admin`) is a comprehensive management console accessible only to authorized phone numbers.

### Admin Tabs

| Tab | Features |
|---|---|
| **Overview** | Stats (users, meetings, projects, revenue), admin wallet, quick metrics |
| **Users** | View/edit/delete users, view profile details, impersonate users ("Login As") |
| **Meetings** | View/edit/delete meetings, status management |
| **Transactions** | View/edit/delete financial transactions |
| **Matches** | View/delete match records |
| **Chats** | View chat messages, delete chats, **broadcast messages to all chats** |
| **Wallets** | View/edit wallet balances, transaction history per wallet |
| **Withdrawals** | Process seeker withdrawal requests (approve/reject), earning history |
| **Delete Requests** | Review and process account deletion requests |

### Admin Special Features
- **Impersonation:** "Login As" any user to view the app as them (opens in new tab)
- **Broadcast Messaging:** Send a message to all active chats
- **Manual Wallet Adjustments:** Edit wallet balances directly
- **Account Deletion Processing:** Approve/reject deletion requests with Firebase Auth cleanup

