## 10. UI/UX Design System

### Brand Colors
| Color | Variable | Value |
|---|---|---|
| Primary | `--primary` | `#22C55E` (Green) |
| Primary Hover | `--primary-hover` | `#16A34A` |
| Background | `--bg-secondary` | Light gray |
| Pastel Green | `--pastel-green` | Soft green tint |

### Design Principles
- **Dark-themed landing page** with gradient and glow effects
- **Light-themed app interface** with pastel green accents
- **Framer Motion** animations throughout (page transitions, tab switches, modals)
- **Spring-based** card swiping physics
- **Bottom sheet** modals for selections
- **Toast notifications** for user feedback
- **Pull-to-refresh** pattern for data updates

---

## 11. Data Model (Firestore Collections)

| Collection | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `seekers` | Seeker user profiles |
| `companies` | Company user profiles |
| `chats` | Chat metadata + `messages` subcollection |
| `meetings` | Meeting records with status tracking |
| `projects` | Project records with timeline |
| `wallets` | User wallet balances |
| `transactions` | Financial transaction records |
| `reviews` | User reviews and ratings |
| `matches` | Like/pass/match records |
| `notifications` | In-app notification records |
| `deleteRequests` | Account deletion requests |
| `withdrawals` | Withdrawal requests from seekers |

---

## 12. Security & Privacy

- **Phone-only auth** — No passwords stored
- **Firebase Security Rules** — Firestore access control
- **Server-side payment verification** — Razorpay signature validation
- **Admin access** — Restricted to specific phone numbers
- **Account deletion** — GDPR-style request/approval flow with full data + auth cleanup
- **reCAPTCHA** — Bot prevention during auth

---

## 13. Deployment & Infrastructure

| Service | Provider |
|---|---|
| Web Hosting | Vercel (production) |
| Database | Firebase Firestore (`plyshipdatabase`) |
| Authentication | Firebase Phone Auth |
| File Storage | Firebase Cloud Storage |
| Payments | Razorpay |
| Mobile Build | Capacitor (Xcode / Android Studio) |
| Domain | plyship.com |

**Deployment Command:** `npx vercel --prod --yes`

---

## 14. Key Metrics to Track

- Total registered users (seekers vs companies)
- Active users (DAU/MAU)
- Meetings scheduled, confirmed, denied
- Projects initiated and completed
- Wallet top-ups and transaction volume
- Average rating per company
- Chat engagement rate
- Swipe-to-meeting conversion rate

